#. Tag: title
#: vfs.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Virtual file systems (VFS)"
msgstr "आभासी सञ्चिकातन्त्राणि (VFS)"

#. Tag: primary
#: vfs.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>VFS</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>VFS</primary> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A basic <link linkend=\"features\">OFM feature</link> is VFS, this an "
"abstracted layer over all kinds of archived information (ZIP files, &FTP; "
"servers, TAR archives, &NFS; filesystems, SAMBA shares, ISO &CD;/&DVD; "
"images, RPM catalogs, &etc;), which allows the user to access all the "
"information in these divergent types of filesystems transparently - just "
"like entering an ordinary sub-folder. &krusader; supports several virtual "
"file systems:"
msgstr ""
"एकः मूलभूतः<link linkend=\"features\"> OFM विशेषता</link> VFS अस्ति, एतत् "
"सर्वविधसंग्रहीतसूचनानाम् (ZIP सञ्चिकाः, &amp;FTP; सर्वरः, TAR संग्रहणः, &amp;NFS; "
"सञ्चिकातन्त्राणि, SAMBA साझाः, ISO &amp;CD;/&amp;DVD; चित्राणि, RPM सूचीपत्राणि, "
"&amp; इत्यादयः) उपरि अमूर्तस्तरः, यत् उपयोक्तारं अनुमतिं ददाति एतेषु विविधप्रकारस्य "
"सञ्चिकातन्त्रेषु सर्वाणि सूचनानि पारदर्शकरूपेण प्राप्तुं - यथा साधारणं उपपुटं प्रविष्टुं । &amp;"
"krusader; अनेकाः आभासीसञ्चिकातन्त्राणि समर्थयति:"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"remote-connections\">Remote connections VFS</link>: provides "
"the capability of working with a remote connection session (&FTP;, &NFS;, "
"Samba, FISH, SFTP) like with local filesystems. It is perfect for complex "
"remote operations and almost as powerful as most standalone &GUI; remote "
"clients."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"remote-connections\">दूरस्थसंयोजनानि VFS</link> : "
"स्थानीयसञ्चिकातन्त्रेषु इव दूरस्थसंयोजनसत्रेण (&amp;FTP;, &amp;NFS;, Samba, FISH, SFTP) "
"सह कार्यं कर्तुं क्षमताम् प्रदाति । इदं जटिलदूरस्थसञ्चालनानां कृते परिपूर्णं भवति तथा च "
"अधिकांशस्य स्वतन्त्रस्य &amp;GUI; दूरस्थग्राहकाः।"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Archive VFS</link>: allows to browse archives in "
"VFS as it was a folder (ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, lha, rar, rpm, tar, "
"zip and 7-zip)."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">अभिलेखागार VFS</link> : VFS मध्ये अभिलेखान् ब्राउज् कर्तुं "
"शक्नोति यतः एतत् एकं समुच्चय आसीत् (ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, lha, rar, "
"rpm, tar, zip तथा 7-zip) ।"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Search VFS</link>: <guibutton>Feed to listbox</"
"guibutton> places the search results in VFS."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">VFS इति अन्वेषणं कुर्वन्तु</link> : १.<guibutton> "
"सूचीपेटिकायां फीड् कुर्वन्तु</guibutton> अन्वेषणपरिणामान् VFS मध्ये स्थापयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Synchronizer VFS</link>: places the "
"synchronizer results in VFS."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"synchronizer\">समन्वयक VFS</link> : समन्वयकपरिणामान् VFS मध्ये "
"स्थापयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Actions you perform on the files in VFS are performed on the 'real' files. "
"You do not just delete files from the VFS - you delete them from your hard "
"drive. Limitations: you cannot create folders inside a VFS."
msgstr ""
"VFS मध्ये सञ्चिकासु भवता क्रियमाणानि क्रियाणि 'वास्तविक' सञ्चिकासु क्रियन्ते । भवान् केवलं "
"VFS तः सञ्चिकाः न विलोपयति - भवान् तान् स्वस्य हार्डड्राइवतः अपास्यति । सीमाः : भवान् "
"VFS इत्यस्य अन्तः पुटं निर्मातुम् न शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to keep the folder structure when doing a copy from a virtual "
"folder to a non virtual folder, by selecting the <quote>Keep virtual folder "
"structure</quote> check box of the copy dialog. Imagine the following "
"virtual folder: <screen><prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>file:/home/myhome/"
"mydir1/myfile1</userinput></screen> <screen><prompt>$</prompt> "
"<userinput>file:/home/myhome/mydir1/myfile2</userinput></screen> "
"<screen><prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>file:/home/myhome/mydir2/myfile3</"
"userinput></screen> Then do the following steps:"
msgstr ""
"आभासीपुटतः अ-आभासीपुटं प्रति प्रतिलिपिं कुर्वन्, प्रतिलिपिसंवादस्य <quote>Keep virtual "
"folder structure</quote> इति चेकबॉक्सं चित्वा, पुटसंरचनां स्थापयितुं शक्यते निम्नलिखित "
"आभासीपुटस्य कल्पनां कुरुत: <screen><prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>file:/home/myhome/"
"mydir1/myfile1</userinput></screen> <screen><prompt>$</prompt> < "
"userinput>सञ्चिका:/home/myhome/mydir1/myfile2</userinput></screen> "
"<screen><prompt>$</prompt> इति <userinput>file:/home/myhome/mydir2/myfile3</"
"userinput></screen> ततः निम्नलिखितपदार्थाः कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "go to the virtual folder and select the files"
msgstr "वर्चुअल् समुच्चय गत्वा सञ्चिकाः चिनोतु"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "select a destination folder (non virtual!)"
msgstr "गन्तव्यपुटं चिनोतु (अ आभासी!) ।"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "press <keycap>F5</keycap>-&gt; copy dialog appears"
msgstr "<keycap>F5</keycap>-&gt; प्रतिलिपिसंवादः दृश्यते"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check <guilabel>Keep virtual folder structure</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>आभासीपुटसंरचनां रक्षतु</guilabel> इति परीक्ष्यताम्"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select <filename>/home/myhome/</filename> for base &URL;"
msgstr "आधारस्य कृते <filename>/home/myhome/</filename> इति चिनोतु &URL;"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start copy by pressing OK"
msgstr "ठीकं नुत्वा प्रतिलिपिं आरभत"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "The result will be:"
msgstr "परिणामः भविष्यति :"

#. Tag: screen
#: vfs.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>destinationdir/mydir1/myfile1</userinput>"
msgstr "<prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>गन्तव्यdir/mydir1/myfile1</userinput>"

#. Tag: screen
#: vfs.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>destinationdir/mydir1/myfile2</userinput>"
msgstr "<prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>गन्तव्यdir/mydir1/myfile2</userinput>"

#. Tag: screen
#: vfs.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>destinationdir/mydir2/myfile3</userinput>"
msgstr "<prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>गन्तव्यdir/mydir2/myfile3</userinput>"
